%20of%20slow%20living.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20city%20dweller%2C%20there's%20one%20thing%20that's%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20do%3A%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20a%20three-day%20trip%20to%20Lazarus%20Island%2C%20a%20small%20island%20five%20miles%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-traveling-to-singapore%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESingapore%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20forced%20to%20slow%20down.%20I%20spent%20one%20night%20in%20a%20glamping%20tent%20on%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebeach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%20February%2C%20Into%20the%20Woods%20is%20an%20accommodation%20that%20promotes%20slow%20living.%20My%20stay%20in%20the%20tent%20was%20380%20Singapore%20dollars%2C%20or%20%24290.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERay%20Lee%20and%20Sam%20Wong%2C%20the%20cofounders%20of%20Into%20the%20Woods%20and%20a%20married%20couple%2C%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20space%20for%20people%20to%20relax%20without%20worrying%20about%20following%20an%20itinerary%20and%20filling%20their%20days%20with%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20had%20enjoyed%20camping%20with%20their%20kids%20while%20living%20abroad%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Australia.%20Despite%20having%20no%20hospitality%20or%20real%20estate%20background%2C%20they%20were%20eager%20to%20start%20something%20similar%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20they%20chanced%20upon%20a%20government%20initiative%20to%20promote%20sustainable%20tourism%20on%20Lazarus%20Island.%20Lee%20and%20Wong%20ended%20up%20winning%20a%20three-year%20tender%20to%20open%20Into%20the%20Woods%20on%20Lazarus%20Island%20in%20March%202023.%20The%20couple%20estimates%20that%20they've%20invested%20almost%20%24800%2C000%20in%20the%20project%20%E2%80%94%20half%20of%20which%20was%20from%20their%20personal%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20guests%20to%20go%20home%20with%20the%20feeling%20of%2C%20'It%20feels%20like%20