0expansive%20space%20to%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20and%20the%2010%20other%20guests%20on%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20nowhere%20to%20eat%20on%20the%20island%2C%20guests%20can%20cook%20their%20own%20meals%20or%20pack%20food.%20I%20pre-ordered%20a%20barbecue%20meat%20set%20for%20around%20%2452%20from%20the%20island's%20convenience%20store.%20It%20came%20with%20enough%20for%20two%20to%20three%20people%20and%20included%20a%20spread%20of%20meat%20skewers%20and%20sausages%2C%20along%20with%20mac%20and%20cheese%20and%20otah%2C%20a%20grilled%20fishcake%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20rare%20opportunity%20to%20cook%20my%20own%20food%20by%20the%20beach%2C%20so%20I%20took%20the%20time%20to%20savor%20each%20bite%20and%20take%20in%20the%20surroundings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20guests%20are%20encouraged%20to%20wash%20their%20own%20dishes%2C%20I%20put%20the%20dirty%20cutlery%20and%20pans%20aside%20to%20haul%20to%20the%20communal%20kitchen%20sink%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224404%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Barbequeing%20meat%20on%20the%20beach%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e3baeed17aa3c7b2b2531c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222973%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGuests%20can%20cook%20their%20meals%20with%20the%20portable%20stove%20and%20cookware%20provided.%3Cp%3EErin%20Liam%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20TV%20and%20a%20spotty%20internet%20connection%2C%20I%20was%20left%20to%20my%20own%20devices%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20evening.%20Thankfully%2C%20each%20room%20has%20a%20doodle%20book%20and%20reflection%20journal%2C%20and%20I%20was%20grateful%20for%20the%20opportunity%20to%20engage%20in%20some%20self-reflection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20latest%20Netflix%20series%20droning%20in%20the%20background%2C%20the%20sound%20of%20the%20waves%20crashing%20onto%20the%20shore%20lu