ate%20Democrats%20are%20trying%20to%20put%20Republicans%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20hot%20seat%20on%20IVF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Senate%20Democrats%20brought%20the%20Right%20to%20IVF%20Act%20to%20a%20second%20vote%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdemocrats-appropriations.house.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fhouse-republicans-refuse-protect-vitro-fertilization-ivf%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWASHINGTON%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520House%2520Appropriations%2520Committee%2520Democrats%2Cand%2520General%2520Government%2520funding%2520bill.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejust%203%20months%20after%20Republicans%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20chamber%20first%20shot%20it%20down.%20The%20bill%20aims%20to%20make%20it%20a%20nationwide%20right%20to%20both%20receive%20and%20provide%20in%20vitro%20fertilization%20services%20and%20includes%20provisions%20to%20make%20it%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Senate%20Republicans%20quickly%20voted%20to%20block%20the%20bill%2C%20which%20they%20have%20previously%20argued%20is%20too%20broad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20JD%20Vance%2C%20the%20Ohio%20senator%20tapped%20as%20Trump's%20VP%20running%20mate%2C%20blasted%20Democrats%20for%20what%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20games.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20and%20Senator%20Vance%20have%20made%20themselves%20crystal%20clear%3A%20They%20fully%20support%20guaranteed%20IVF%20access%20for%20every%20American%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20spokesperson%20Taylor%20Van%20Kirk%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20unfortunate%20that%20Chuck%20Schumer%20chose%20to%20play%20political%20games%20with%20the%20Senate's%20time%20instead%20of%20working%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20crushing%20inflation%20that%20Kamala%20Harris%20created.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20colleagues%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20reintroduce%20the%20bill%20was%20influenced%20by%20Trump's%20own%20recent%20endorsements%20of%20IVF%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fsenate-ivf-vote-republicans-trump%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20an%20apparent%20attempt%20to%20pressure%20Trump%20to%20stand%20by%20his%20promise%20to%20support%20IVF%20and%20urge%20his%20Republican%20colleagues%20to%20vote%20in%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20last%20week's%20debate%20against%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20the%20former%20president%20called%20himself%20a%20%26quot%3Bleader%20on%20IVF.%26quot%3B%20And%20in%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump%2Ftrump-says-wants-make-ivf-treatments-paid-government-insurance-compani-rcna168804%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20told%20NBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20if%20reelected%2C%20he%20would%20protect%20the%20right%20to%20IVF%20and%20get%20the%20costs%20covered%20for%20Americans%20who%20need%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Democrats%20have%20accused%20Trump%20of%20making%20false%20promises%2C%20using%20statements%20from%20his%20running%20mate%2C%20Vance%2C%20that%20disparaged%20women%20without%20children%20and%20supported%20abortion%20bans%20to%20allege%20Trump%20won't%20follow%20through%20with%20his%20campaign%20vow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20Tuesday's%20vote%2C%20Democrats%20argued%20that%20if%20Trump%20wanted%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20that%20promise%2C%20all%20he%20needed%20to%20do%20was%20say%20the%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Republicans%20want%20to%20protect%20people's%20right%20to%20access%20IVF%2C%20they%20can%20vote%20yes%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Illinois%20Sen.%20Tammy%20Duckworth%2C%20who%20sponsored%20the%20legislation%2C%20told%20CBS%20News.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20shown%20that%20it%20only%20takes%20one%20sentence%20from%20him%2C%20and%20the%20Republican%20Party%20will%20fall%20in%20line%20behind%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20campai