p%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20collegiate%20model%20changes%2C%20we%20have%20to%20remain%20flexible%2C%26quot%3B%20UT's%20athletics%20director%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_JztRtFwK_k%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDanny%20White%20said%20in%20a%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20explaining%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20price%20hike.%20%26quot%3BThat%20connection%20between%20resources%20and%20competitiveness%20has%20never%20been%20tighter.%20Only%20now%2C%20we%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20share%20these%20resources%20with%20our%20athletes.%20We%20can%20generate%20revenue%20that%20will%20go%20directly%20to%20our%20players.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20the%2010%25%20talent%20fee%2C%20the%20university%20also%20announced%20that%202025%20ticket%20prices%20will%20be%20increasing%204.5%25%20per%20seat%20on%20average.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20tickets%20will%20shoot%20up%20a%20total%20of%2014.5%25%20on%20average%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20be%20a%20leader%20in%20college%20sports.%20That%20means%20we%20want%20to%20be%20a%20leader%20in%20revenue%20sharing%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20football%20fans%20aren't%20footing%20the%20entire%20cost%20of%20revenue%20sharing%20%E2%80%94%20only%20a%20portion%20of%20it.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20UT%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20talent%20fee%20will%20help%20cover%20about%2033%25%20of%20the%20total%20cost%20of%20paying%20players.%20The%20university%20will%20be%20fronting%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20annual%20%2422%20million%20revenue-sharing%20pool%20to%20pay%20athletes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.knoxnews.com%2Fstory%2Fsports%2Fcollege%2Funiversity-of-tennessee%2Ffootball%2F2024%2F09%2F17%2Ftennessee-football-ticket-price-increase-2025-pay-players-revenue-sharing-nil%2F75085214007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKnox%20News%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUT's%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20made%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20settlement%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-ncaa-third-party-endorsement-startups-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHouse%20v.%20NCAA%20federal%20antitrust%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20go%20into%20effect%20as%20early%20as%20July%202025.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20May%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-college-sports-change-donor-fatigue-nil-recruiting-student-athletes-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20NCAA%20and%20five%20major%20conferences%20agreed%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20revenue-sharing%20model%20that%20would%20pay%20student-athletes%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20revenue%20their%20colleges%20make%20from%20ticket%20sales%2C%20broadcast%20deals%2C%20and%20merch%20bearing%20an%20athlete's%20name%2C%20image%2C%20and%20likeness%20(known%20as%20NIL).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20deal%20has%20since%20gone%20back%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbssports.com%2Fcollege-football%2Fnews%2Fwhats-next-for-ncaa-nil-collectives-after-house-settlement-talks-hit-roadblock-from-federal-judge%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520%25242.8%2520billion%2520settlement%2520in%2Csettlement%2520is%2520transformative%2520for%2520players.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einto%20negotiations%20after%20the%20judge%20overseeing%20the%20case%20paused%3C%2Fa%3E%20preliminary%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20also%20preparing%20for%20additional%20financial%20aid%2C%20potential%20compliance%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20other%20resource%20development%20costs%20that%20are%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20associated%20with%20the%20proposed%20House%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UT%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BThese%20include%20new%20scholarships%2C%20taxes%2C%20fair%20market%20value%20assessment%2C%20reporting%2C%20and%20other%20unknown%20business%20and%20legal%20assessments%20that%20may%20be%20required.%26quot