%20posture%20management%20can%20help%20identify%20risks%20and%20protect%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fsecurity-playbook%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESecurity%20Playbook%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20detailing%20cybersecurity%20advice%20and%20strategies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20handle%20troves%20of%20data%2C%20including%20financial%20information%2C%20customer%20details%2C%20and%20proprietary%20content.%20While%20much%20of%20that%20data%20is%20stored%20in%20the%20cloud%2C%20company%20leaders%20might%20not%20always%20know%20exactly%20where%20it%20is%2C%20who%20all%20has%20access%20to%20it%2C%20or%20how%20secure%20it%20truly%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20Benjamin%2C%20the%20senior%20director%20of%20product%20management%20at%20Prisma%20Cloud%2C%20a%20cloud-security%20platform%20made%20by%20Palo%20Alto%20Networks%2C%20said%20that%20incorporating%20data-security%20posture%20management%20into%20cybersecurity%20strategies%20could%20help%20solve%20many%20of%20these%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20DSPM%20as%20a%20set%20of%20cybersecurity%20technologies%20that%20can%20help%20companies%20%26quot%3Bdiscover%2C%20understand%2C%20and%20protect%20their%20data.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20crucial%2C%20as%20an%20IBM%20report%20published%20in%202023%20estimated%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibm.com%2Ftopics%2Fdata-security-posture-management%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E82%25%20of%20data%20breaches%3C%2Fa%3E%20involved%20data%20stored%20in%20the%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClouds%20and%20the%20data%20they%20contain%20are%20vulnerable%20for%20several%20reasons.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20Benjamin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20sheer%20amount%20of%20data%20in%20the%20cloud%20is%20larger%20than%20the%20amount%20of%20data%20that's%20on-premises%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fartificial-intelligence-data-privacy-on-premises-information-technology-solutions-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estored%20on%20a%20company's%20own%20hardware%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Organizations%20also%20often%20use%20several%20cloud%20systems%20and%20sometimes%20lack%20a%20solid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-wang-talks-artificial-intelligence-and-on-premises-infrastructure-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20strategy%20for%20maintaining%2C%20updating%2C%20and%20securing%20data%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiat%20Hayun%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20product%20management%20and%20research%20of%20cloud%20security%20at%20the%20cybersecurity%20company%20Tenable%2C%20said%20cloud%20environments'%20flexibility%20makes%20them%20attractive%20to%20companies.%20Clouds%20make%20it%20easy%20for%20companies%20to%20store%20and%20move%20data%20around%2C%20but%20they're%20also%20difficult%20to%20monitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20DSPM%20can%20help%2C%20Hayun%20said%2C%20many%20organizations%20haven't%20embraced%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22500962ef-2e5d-401c-aa84-3745209e9825%5C%22%3EHow%20DSPM%20safeguards%20data%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20said%20DSPM%20helps%20organizations%20answer%20three%20key%20questions%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20data%20do%20I%20have%3F%20How%20is%20it%20being%20used%3F%20And%20how%20is%20it%20being%20protected%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHayun%20said%20the%20software%20continuously%20identifies%20where%20a%20company's%20data%20resides%20and%20classifies%20it%20based%20on%20its%20sensitivity%20level%2C%20such%20as%20personally%20identifiable%20information%20or%20intellectual%20property.%20It%20then%20analyzes%20the%20controls%20around%20the%20data%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-respond-to-ransomware-attack%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20has%20access%20to%20it%20and%20how%20secure%20it%20is%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20identifies%20vulnerabilities%3B%20and%20recommends%20ways%20to%20address%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJulie%20Madhusoodanan%2C%20the%20head%20of%20cybersecurity%20at%20LinkedIn%2C%20described%20DSPM%20as%20a%20combination%20of%20risk%20identification%2C%20reporting%2C%20and%20mitigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20of%20it%20as%20having%20a%20security%20guard%20who%20regularly%20checks%20where%20your%20data%20is%20stored%2C%20who%20has%20access%20to%20it%2C%20and%20how%20it's%20being%20used%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20something%20looks%20off%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20sensitive%20information%20is%20being%20stored%20in%20the%20wrong%20place%2C%20or%20someone%20has%20access%20to%20data%20they%20shouldn't%20have%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0DSPM%20software%20can%20alert%20a%20company's%20security%20or%20information-technology%20teams%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20%26quot%3Bbefore%20something%20bad%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20Madhusoodanan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20cybersecurity%20solutions%20focus%20on%20securing%20devices%20or%20systems%20that%20house%20or%20process%20data%20and%20often%20identify%20vulnerabilities%20and%20risks%20after%20they%20happen.%20Madhusoodanan%20said%20DSPM%20is%20designed%20to%20protect%20the%20data%20itself%20and%20%26quot%3Bcan%20proactively%20block%20risks%20from%20being%20inserted%20into%20the%20system%20in%20the%20first%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238f8e7b1-fe20-45f3-ac0f-8e4e65aafba3%5C%22%3EWhy%20DSPM%20is%20a%20beneficial%20security%20measure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20organization%20that%20collects%2C%20maintains%2C%20and%20processes%20data%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20its%20size%20or%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-about-sec-cybersecurity-rules-and-guidance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20risk%20of%20a%20breach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Madhusoodanan%20said.%20Investing%20in%20DSPM%2C%20she%20added%2C%20can%20help%20%26quot%3Bgive%20organizations%20a%20clearer%20picture%20of%20the%20risk%20their%20business%20is%20carrying%2C%26quot%3B%20manage%20that%20risk%2C%20and%20heighten%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20LinkedIn%20uses%20DSPM%20to%20assess%20threats%20and%20plan%20mitigation%20strategies.%20Madhusoodanan%20said%20the%20technology%20had%20improved%20the%20company's%20response%20time%20and%20accuracy%20in%20addressing%20vulnerabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20gave%20an%20example%20of%20a%20financial%20company%20he%20worked%20with%3A%20It%20used%20DSPM%20and%20discovered%20that%20some%20financial%20reports%20were%20being%20copied%20to%20a%20cloud%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-companies-can-respond-to-cybersecurity-risks-after-layoffs-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebelonged%20to%20a%20former%20employee%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20tool%20identified%20the%20issue%20so%20the%20company%20could%20secure%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20said%20DSPM%20could%20also%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20and%20impact%20of%20a%20data%20breach.%20Breaches%20can%20cost%20a%20company%20millions%20of%20dollars%2C%20damage%20its%20reputation%2C%20interfere%20with%20operations%2C%20and%20cause%20compliance%20problems%20if%20sensitive%20data%20is%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHayun%20said%20DSPM%20could%20ensure%20that%20companies%20don't%20take%20unnecessary%20risks%20with%20data%20and%20make%20them%20feel%20more%20secure%20in%20scaling%20up%20their%20data%20programs%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20grow%20their%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20said%20that%20while%20DSPM%20could%20benefit%20most%20companies%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20especially%20advantageous%20for%20those%20in%20regulated%20industries%2C%20such%20as%20finance%20or%20health%2C%20or%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20customer%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22087ddab0-b09f-4ff6-b341-21bcf3c50adf%5C%22%3ESome%20companies%20face%20challenges%20implementing%20DSPM%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20implementing%20DSPM%20tech%20can%20struggle%20with%20hiring%20the%20appropriate%20staff%2C%20lacking%20internal%20resources%2C%20selecting%20a%20DSPM%20vendor%20or%20tool%2C%20and%20getting%20executive%20buy-in%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnormalyze.ai%2Fcompany%2Ffrom-reactive-to-proactive-dspms-transformative-role-in-data-security%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20from%20Normalyze%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20DSPM%20provider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMadhusoodanan%20said%20that%20DSPM%20strategies%20can't%20be%20implemented%20in%20silos%20and%20that%20stakeholder%20buy-in%20is%20critical.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20leaders%20face%20the%20biggest%20friction%20and%20why%20fostering%20a%20security-centric%20culture%20is%20key%20to%20getting%20leaders%20on%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20it's%20essential%20to%20ensure%20everyone%20across%20an%20organization%20understands%20and%20is%20focused%20on%20the%20company's%20data-protection%20strategies%20so%20that%20the%20organization%20can%20make%20accurate%20risk-mitigation%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHayun%20said%20DSPM%20enabled%20organizations%20to%20use%20data%20effectively%20and%20securely%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20compliance%20with%20regulatory%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20can%20build%20guardrails%20around%20how%20the%20data%20is%20used%20and%20allow%20their%20teams%20to%20run%20within%20those%20guardrails%20without%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-data-security-posture-management%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726596925000%2C%22visual