a%20decades-long%20scheme%20of%20sex%20trafficking%20and%20racketeering%2C%20according%20to%20a%20three-count%20federal%20indictment%20unsealed%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20in%202009%2C%20Combs%20used%20his%20vast%20media%20empire%20including%20his%20record%20label%20Bad%20Boy%20Entertainment%20to%20transport%20women%2C%20as%20well%20as%20male%20sex%20workers%2C%20across%20state%20lines%20to%20take%20part%20in%20recorded%20sexual%20performances%20called%20%26quot%3BFreak%20Offs%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20the%20music%20mogul%20would%20watch%20and%20masturbate%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2054-year-old%20rapper%20and%20producer%20was%20arrested%20in%20Manhattan%20on%20Monday%20night%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20before%20US%20Magistrate%20Judge%20Robyn%20Tarnofsky%20at%202%3A30%20pm%20EDT%20(1830%20GMT)%20on%20Tuesday.%20Combs%20could%20face%20decades%20in%20prison%20if%20convicted%20of%20the%20three%20felony%20counts%20he%20faces%3A%20racketeering%20conspiracy%2C%20sex%20trafficking%2C%20and%20transportation%20to%20engage%20in%20prostitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charges%20were%20brought%20by%20the%20office%20of%20Manhattan%20US%20Attorney%20Damian%20Williams%2C%20which%20is%20seeking%20to%20have%20Combs%20remain%20detained%20pending%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombs%20enticed%20women%20by%20giving%20them%20drugs%20such%20as%20ketamine%20and%20ecstasy%2C%20financial%20support%2C%20or%20promises%20of%20career%20support%20or%20a%20romantic%20relationship%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%20Combs%20then%20used%20surreptitious%20recordings%20of%20the%20sex%20acts%20as%20%26quot%3Bcollateral%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20women%20would%20remain%20silent%2C%20and%20sometimes%20displayed%20weapons%20to%20intimidate%20abuse%20victims%20and%20witnesses%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20victims%20did%20not%20believe%20they%20could%20refuse%20Combs%20without%20risking%20their%20security%20or%20facing%20more%20abuse%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20told%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20contained%20no%20allegation%20that%20Combs%20himself%20directly%20engaged%20in%20unwanted%20sexual%20contact%20with%20women%2C%20though%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20assaulting%20women%20by%20punching%20them%20or%20throwing%20objects%20at%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20MUSIC%20ICON'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarc%20Agnifilo%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Combs%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20after%20the%20indictment%20was%20made%20public%2C%20but%20on%20Monday%20night%20expressed%20disappointment%20with%20the%20decision%20to%20pursue%20an%20%26quot%3Bunjust%26quot%3B%20prosecution%20of%20his%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSean%20'Diddy'%20Combs%20is%20a%20music%20icon%2C%20self-made%20entrepreneur%2C%20loving%20family%20man%2C%20and%20proven%20philanthropist%20who%20has%20spent%20the%20last%2030%20years%20building%20an%20empire%2C%20adoring%20his%20children%2C%20and%20working%20to%20uplift%20the%20Black%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Agnifilo%20said%20on%20Monday%20night.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20an%20imperfect%20person%2C%20but%20he%20is%20not%20a%20criminal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombs%20is%20the%20highest-profile%20person%20in%20the%20music%20industry%20to%20face%20criminal%20charges%20for%20sexual%20misconduct%20since%20R.%20Kelly%2C%20the%20R%26amp%3BB%20singer.%20Kelly%20was%20sentenced%20to%20a%20combined%2031%20years%20in%20prison%20after%20being%20convicted%20in%20New%20York%20in%202021%20and%20Chicago%20in%202022%20on%20charges%20including%20sex%20trafficking%2C%20racketeering%20and%20child%20sex%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20known%20during%20his%20career%20as%20P.%20Diddy%20and%20Puff%20Daddy%2C%20Combs%20founded%20Bad%20Boy%20records%20and%20is%20credited%20with%20helping%20turn%20rappers%20and%20R%26amp%3BB%20singers%20such%20as%20Mary%20J.%20Blige%2C%20Faith%20Evans%2C%20Notorious%20B.I.G.%20and%20Usher%20into%20stars%20in%20the%201990s%20and%202000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20career%20and%20reputation%20have%20been%20marred%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20Last%20November%2C%20his%20former%20girlfriend%20Casandra%20Ventura%2C%20an%20R%26amp%3BB%20singer%20known%20as%20Cassie%2C%20accused%20him%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20of%20serial%20physical%20abuse%2C%20sexual%20slavery%20and%20rape%20during%20their%20decade-long%20relationship.%20She%20agreed%20to%20an%20undisclosed%20settlement%20one%20day%20after%20suing%2C%20even%20as%20Combs%20denied%20her%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombs%20has%20since%20faced%20several%20other%20civil%20lawsuits%20by%20women%20and%20men%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20other%20misconduct.%20His%20lawyers%20have%20been%20fighting%20those%20cases%20in%20court.%20Federal%20agents%20raided%20Combs'%20homes%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20Miami%20Beach%2C%20Florida%20six%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBABY%20OIL%2C%20AR-15%20RIFLES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmployees%20of%20Combs%20helped%20arrange%20the%20%26quot%3BFreak%20Offs%26quot%3B%20by%20booking%20hotel%20rooms%20and%20buying%20controlled%20substances%20and%20other%20items%20used%20during%20sex%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20found%20drugs%20and%201%2C000%20bottles%20of%20baby%20oil%20and%20lubricant%20during%20searches%20of%20Combs'%20homes%20in%20Miami%2C%20Florida%20and%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20along%20with%20AR-15%20rifles%20with%20defaced%20serial%20numbers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20did%20not%20specify%20how%20many%20women%20were%20alleged%20victims%20of%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20charges%20are%20not%20Combs'%20first%20brush%20with%20the%20law.%20He%20was%20acquitted%20in%20March%202001%20of%20bribery%20and%20weapons%20charges%20in%20a%20criminal%20trial%20stemming%20from%20a%20nightclub%20shooting%20that%20left%20three%20people%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20lawsuits%20that%20Combs%20faces%20include%20a%20case%20filed%20last%20week%20by%20the%20singer%20Dawn%20Richard%2C%20formerly%20of%20Danity%20Kane%2C%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20battery%2C%20sex%20trafficking%2C%20gender%20discrimination%20and%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20this%20month%2C%20a%20Michigan%20judge%20ordered%20Combs%20to%20pay%20a%20%24100%20million%20default%20judgment%20to%20Derrick%20Lee%20Smith%2C%20who%20said%20Combs%20drugged%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20him%20at%20a%20party%20almost%2030%20years%20ago.%20A%20lawyer%20for%20Combs%20said%20he%20would%20seek%20a%20dismissal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECombs%20has%20also%20denied%20claims%20in%20a%20February%20sex%20trafficking%20lawsuit%20by%20Rodney%20%26quot%3BLil%20Rod%26quot%3B%20Jones%2C%20who%20Combs%20employed%20as%20a%20producer%20on%20his%202023%20release%20%26quot%3BThe%20Love%20Album%3A%20Off%20the%20Grid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726594620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fvgmfpskg_sean-combs_625x300_17_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-rapper-sean-diddy-combs-charged-with-racketeering-sex-trafficking-6588528%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs%20used%20his%20fame%20as%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20in%20hip-hop%20to%20coerce%20women%20into%20engaging%20in%20demeaning%20sex%20acts%20as%20part%20of%20a%20decades-long%20scheme%20of%20sex%20trafficking%20and%20racketeering%2C%20according%20to%20a%20federal%20indictment%20unsealed%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fwor