ndependent%20war%20monitor%20has%20said%20that%20fourteen%20people%20have%20also%20been%20injured%20in%20pager%20blasts%20in%20Syria%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%2C%20which%20is%20banned%20both%20by%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20is%20the%20political%20and%20military%20establishment%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20is%20backed%20by%20Iran.%20Hezbollah%20backs%20Hamas%2C%20which%20has%20been%20at%20war%20with%20Israel%20in%20Gaza%20since%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Saudi%20news%20channel%20Al%20Hadath%2C%20the%20pager%20attacks%20have%20killed%20a%20son%20of%20Ali%20Ammar%2C%20the%20Hezbollah%20representative%20in%20the%20Lebanese%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20reports%20claim%20that%20the%20explosions%20were%20caused%20due%20to%20the%20overheating%20of%20lithium%20batteries%20caused%20by%20an%20electronic%20signal%20breach%20(quite%20like%20a%20cyber%20attack)%2C%20some%20other%20reports%20allege%20that%20a%20thin%20lining%20of%20explosives%20were%20placed%20inside%20the%20pagers%20before%20being%20supplied.%20%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20cannot%20independently%20verify%20either%20of%20these%20claims%20at%20the%20moment%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20has%20blamed%20Israel%20for%20the%20attack%20and%20has%20claimed%20that%20this%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20security%20breach%26quot%3B%20it%20has%20faced%20yet.%20All%20the%20pagers%20exploded%20nearly%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Hezbollah%20has%20claimed%2C%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20an%20%26quot%3BIsraeli%20breach%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20communications%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Irans%20Ambassador%20to%20Lebanon%20Mojtaba%20Amani%20has%20been%20injured%20in%20the%20incident%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Irans%20Ambassador%20to%20Lebanon%20Mojtaba%20Amani%20has%20been%20injured%20in%20the%20incident%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F2ree8uss_mojtaba-amani-iran-ambassador-to-lebanon_625x300_17_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran's%20Ambassador%20to%20Lebanon%20Mojtaba%20Amani%20has%20been%20injured%20in%20the%20incident%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20strongholds%20across%20Lebanon%20have%20been%20hit%20by%20the%20%26quot%3BIsraeli%20breach%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20such%20major%20incident%20since%20the%20group%20began%20trading%20fire%20with%20Israel%20almost%20every%20day%20in%20its%20support%20for%20Hamas%20which%20is%20at%20war%20with%20Israel%20in%20Gaza%20since%20the%20October%207%20%26quot%3Bterror%20attack%26quot%3B%20targeting%20Israeli%20nationals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20explosions%20happened%20outside%20Lebanon%20too%2C%20as%20four%20people%20were%20injured%20in%20Syria%20as%20at%20least%20one%20pager%20blew%20up%20in%20a%20vehicle%20in%20Damascus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDozens%20of%20Hezbollah%20members%20have%20been%20wounded%20in%20the%20south%20and%20in%20Beirut's%20southern%20suburbs%20after%20their%20pagers%20exploded%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20source%20close%20to%20Hezbollah%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP%2C%20requesting%20anonymity%20to%20discuss%20sensitive%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELebanon's%20official%20National%20News%20Agency%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20unprecedented%20enemy%20security%20incident%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3Bhandheld%20pagers%20detonating%26quot%3B%20at%20nearly%20the%20same%20time%20across%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20AFP%2C%20Hezbollah%20communicates%20through%20its%20own%20telecommunications%20system%20and%20has%20asked%20its%20members%20to%20avoid%20using%20mobile%20phones%20since%20the%20Gaza%20war%20began%20almost%20a%20year%20ago.%20The%20diktat%20was%20issued%20to%20avoid%20Israeli%20breaches%20of%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHEZBOLLAH%20BLAMES%20ISRAEL%20IN%20STATEMENT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20put%20out%20a%20statement%20shortly%20after%20the%20pager%20explosions%20saying%20that%20at%20%26quot%3BAround%203%3A30%20pm%20(local%20time)%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20several%20pager%20devices%20used%20by%20Hezbollah%20members%20and%20officials%20of%20various%20institutions%20exploded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20is%20fully%20responsible%20for%20the%20pager%20blasts%2C%26quot%3B%20Hezbollah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20further%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20girl%20and%20her%20two%20brothers%26quot%3B%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20while%20many%20others%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20relevant%20authorities%20in%20Hezbollah%20are%20currently%20conducting%20extensive%20security%20and%20scientific%20investigations%20to%20find%20the%20reasons%20for%20these%20simultaneous%20explosions%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20urged%20people%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bcautious%20of%20rumors%20and%20misinformation%20spread%20by%20certain%20parties%2C%20as%20this%20may%20serve%20the%20psychological%20warfare%26quot%3B%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20these%20claims%20made%20by%20Hezbollah%20or%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20A%20PAGER%3F%20HOW%20DOES%20IT%20WORK%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20pager%20is%20an%20electronic%20telecommunications%20device%20which%20were%20mostly%20used%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20early%202000s%20to%20send%20text%20and%20alpha-numeric%20messages.%20Pagers%20usually%20beep%2C%20vibrate%2C%20or%20flash%20short%20text%20notifications%20to%20alert%20or%20update%20the%20end%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPagers%2C%20also%20known%20as%20beepers%20or%20bleepers%2C%20is%20a%20wireless%20communications%20device%20that%20receives%20and%20displays%20alphanumeric%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20voice%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20various%20types%20of%20pagers%20-%20A%20one-way%20pager%20can%20only%20receive%20messages%2C%20while%20a%20two-way%20or%20'response'%20pagers%20can%20also%20respond.%20The%20response%20also%20is%20an%20alpha-numeric%20text%20which%20acknowledges%20or%20replies%20to%20the%20original%20message%20using%20an%20internal%20transmitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo-way%20pagers%2C%20also%20known%20as%20response%20pagers%20typically%20work%20using%20ReFLEX%20protocol%2C%20which%20was%20developed%20in%20the%20mid-1990s%20by%20Motorola%20Corp.%20FLEX%20provides%20one-way%20communication%20only%20(from%20the%20provider%20to%20the%20pager%20device)%2C%20but%20a%20related%20protocol%20called%20ReFLEX%20provides%20two-way%20messaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModern%20paging%20systems%20typically%20use%20multiple%20base%20transmitters%20to%20modulate%20the%20same%20signal%20on%20the%20same%20RF%20or%20Radio%20Frequency%20channel%2C%20a%20design%20approach%20called%20simulcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20transmitted%20over%20FLEX%20and%20ReFLEX%20is%20not%20encrypted%20and%20is%20hence%20vulnerable%20to%20breaches.%20There%20are%20codes%20used%20to%20improve%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20data%2C%20but%20these%20are%20not%20cryptographically%20secure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20encryption%20methods%20were%20being%20used%20by%20the%20Hezbollah%20is%20not%20known.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726592400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F6dtgtu9g_hezbollah-pagers-explode-lebanon-pagers-explode_625x300_17_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthousands-of-pagers-explode-in-lebanon-several-members-injured-in-biggest-security-breach-says-hezbollah-6587184%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%228%20people%20have%20died%20and%20more%20than%202%2C750%20injured%2C%20many%20grievously%20so%2C%20in%20Lebanon%20in%20a%20synchronised%20detonation%20of%20pagers%20targeting%20US-designated%20terror%20group%20Hezbollah.%20Iran's%20state%20media%20reported%20that%20its%20Ambassador%20to%20Lebanon%20has%20also%20been%20w