ch%20it%20has%20inherited%20from%20its%20predecessor%20Jan%20Sangh%2C%20Mr%20Meghwal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20fulfilled%20the%20other%20two%20promises%20--%20the%20construction%20of%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Constitution's%20Article%20370%20that%20gave%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20its%20special%20status...%20The%20Law%20Commission%20is%20working%20on%20it%20(the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code)%20%2C%20but%20some%20states%20have%20already%20implemented%20it...%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Goa.%20Other%20states%20are%20thinking%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Meghwal%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20minister%2C%20he%20added%2C%20has%20declared%20it%20from%20the%20ramparts%20of%20the%20Red%20Fort%20in%20his%20address%20on%20Independence%20Day.%20We%20will%20talk%20to%20the%20allies%20and%20certainly%20take%20steps%20in%20his%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20which%20will%20do%20away%20with%20personal%20laws%20of%20various%20communities%20on%20key%20issues%20like%20marriage%2C%20divorce%2C%20inheritance%2C%20and%20adoption%2C%20and%20bring%20all%20citizens%20on%20par%2C%20has%20been%20bitterly%20criticized%20by%20the%20Opposition%2C%20given%20its%20current%20form.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20NDA%20allies%20--%20among%20them%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minster%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20his%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20counterpart%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20--%20are%20also%20on%20the%20same%20page%20as%20the%20Opposition.%20%C2%A0Both%20parties%20have%20called%20for%20wider%20discussions%20and%20consensus%20on%20the%20law%20before%20it%20is%20given%20a%20final%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20bill%20is%20now%20before%20a%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20committee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20Independence%20Day%20address%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20called%20the%20current%20criminal%20law%20%26quot%3Bcommunal%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20should%20be%20replaced%20by%20secular%20version.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20people%20in%20the%20country%20--and%20it%20is%20true%20--%20believe%20that%20the%20Civil%20Code%20we%20currently%20follow%20is%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20a%20communal%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20imperative%20that%20we%20establish%20a%20Secular%20Civil%20Code%20in%20the%20country...%20only%20then%20can%20we%20eliminate%20discrimination%20based%20on%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20also%20called%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20in%20several%20of%20its%20judgments.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726577340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Forghdh7g_arjun-ram-meghwal-ndtv_625x300_18_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-discuss-with-allies-law-minister-arjun-meghwal-on-uniform-civil-code-6586049%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20will%20come%20and%20the%20BJP%20will%20talk%20to%20NDA%20allies%20to%20make%20it%20happen%2C%20Union%20minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20told%20NDTV%20on%20the%20100-day%20anniversary%20of%20the%20third%20consecutive%20government%20headed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-discuss-with-allies-law-minister-arjun-meghwal-on-uniform-civil-code-6586049%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women's%20T20%20WC%20Prize%20Money%20Now%20Equal%20To%20Men's%2C%20Sees%20134%25%20Rise%20To...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20on%20Tuesday%20announced%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20men%20and%20women%20in%20World%20Cups%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20women's%20T20%20showpiece%20in%20the%20UAE%20next%20month.%20The%20winners%20of%20the%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20will%20be%20rewarded%20with%20USD%202.34%20million%2C%20a%20134%20per%20cent%20increase%20on%20the%20USD%201%20million%20awarded%20to%20Australian%20women%20when%20they%20clinched%20the%20title%20in%20South%20Africa%20in%202023%2C%20said%20the%20ICC%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20will%20be%20the%20first%20ICC%20event%20where%20women%20will%20receive%20the%20same%20prize%20money%20as%20their%20male%20counterparts%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20the%20sport's%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20the%20ICC%20Annual%20Conference%20in%20July%202023%2C%20when%20the%20ICC%20Board%20took%20the%20step%20of%20reaching%20its%20prize%20money%20equity%20target%20seven%20years%20ahead%20of%20its%20schedule%20of%202030%2C%20making%20cricket%20the%20only%20major%20team%20sport%20to%20have%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20its%20men's%20and%20women's%20World%20Cup%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20runners-up%20at%20the%20showpiece%20event%20next%20month%20will%20get%20USD%201.17%20million%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20134%20per%20cent%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20USD%20500%2C000%20South%20Africa%20received%20for%20reaching%20the%20final%20on%20home%20soil%20at%20Newlands%20Cricket%20Ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20losing%20semi-finalists%20will%20earn%20USD%20675%2C%20000%20(up%20from%20USD%20210%20000%20in%202023)%2C%20with%20the%20overall%20prize%20pot%20totalling%20USD%207%2C958%2C080%2C%20a%20massive%20increase%20of%20225%20per%20cent%20from%20last%20year's%20total%20fund%20of%20USD%202.45%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20win%20during%20the%20group%20stages%20will%20see%20teams%20take%20home%20USD%2031%2C154%2C%20while%20the%20six%20teams%20who%20fail%20to%20reach%20the%20semi-finals%20will%20share%20a%20pool%20of%20USD%201.35%20million%20depending%20on%20their%20finishing%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20equivalent%20pool%20for%20the%20six%20teams%20in%202023%20was%20USD%20180%2C000%2C%20shared%20equally.%20Teams%20who%20finish%20third%20or%20fourth%20in%20their%20group%20will%20take%20USD%20270%2C000%20each%20while%20the%20teams%20who%20finish%20fifth%20in%20their%20group%20will%20both%20receive%20USD%20135%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20move%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20ICC's%20strategy%20to%20prioritise%20the%20women's%20game%20and%20accelerate%20its%20growth%20by%202032.%20Teams%20will%20now%20receive%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20the%20equivalent%20finishing%20position%20at%20comparable%20events%20as%20well%20as%20the%20same%20amount%20for%20winning%20a%20match%20at%20those%20events%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ICC%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726575240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F0k3anp78_smriti-mandhana_625x300_28_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwomens-t20-world-cup-2024-prize-money-now-equal-to-mens-sees-134-rise-to-6584784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20on%20Tuesday%20announced%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20men%20and%20women%20in%20World%20Cups%2C%20starting%20with%20the%20women's%20T20%20showpiece%20in%20the%20UAE%20next%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwomens-t20-world-cup-2024-prize-money-now-equal-to-mens-sees-134-rise-to-6584784%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Melania%2C%20Jill%2C%20Michelle%2C%20Hillary%20met%20last%20year%3A%20'First%20Ladies%20are%20not%20mean%20girls'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726574410000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113428055%2Cimgsize-605339.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.ind