NDTV%20as%20Modi%203.0%20completed%20100%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20took%20historic%20initiatives%20in%20the%20first%20and%20second%20terms%20and%20set%20the%20foundation%20for%20India%20to%20become%20a%20developed%20country%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20election%20process%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20called%20all%20the%20bureaucrats%20and%20told%20them%20that%20the%20country's%20progress%20should%20not%20stop.%20He%20told%20the%20officials%20that%20we%20would%20be%20busy%20with%20elections%2C%20but%20they%20should%20keep%20planning.%20Because%20of%20this%20vision%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20announce%20many%20new%20programmes%20and%20start%20new%20work%20in%20100%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E100-Day%20Report%20Card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20his%20ministry%20has%20performed%20in%20the%20first%20100%20days%20of%20Modi%203.0%2C%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20said%20Railways%20has%20started%2012%20new%20projects%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railways%20Minister%20said%20the%20government%20is%20focusing%20on%20improving%20the%20travel%20experience%20of%20lower-income%20and%20middle-income%20groups.%20He%20said%20they%20are%20adding%20general%20coaches%20that%20cater%20to%20lower-income%20groups.%20%26quot%3B108%20trains%20have%20been%20augmented%20with%20new%20general%20coaches%20and%2012%2C500%20new%20general%20coaches%20are%20being%20manufactured%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20NaMo%20Bharat%20Rapid%20Rail%20service%2C%20the%20first%20of%20which%20was%20inaugurated%20between%20Ahmedabad%20and%20Bhuj%20yesterday%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20going%20to%20be%20revolutionary%20because%2C%20at%20a%20very%20low%20cost%2C%20a%20very%20high-quality%20service%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20commuters%20travelling%20from%20one%20city%20to%20another.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Railways'%20infrastructure%20push%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20the%20world's%20highest%20rail%20arch%20bridge%2C%20Chenab%20Bridge%2C%20has%20been%20commissioned%2C%20900%20km%20of%20new%20tracks%20commissioned%2C%20and%20100%20digital%20stations%20and%20309%20locomotives%20are%20in%20the%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaishnaw%20said%20the%20Railways%20has%20introduced%20a%20direct%20drive%20technology%20based%20on%20the%20lessons%20learned%20from%20the%20Balasore%20accident%20that%20left%20nearly%20300%20people%20dead.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Balasore%20accident%2C%20there%20was%20manipulation%20in%20the%20electrical%20panel%20that%20controls%20point%20machines%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20change%20the%20entire%20technology.%20The%20first%20direct%20drive%20technology%20has%20now%20been%20introduced%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20said%20that%2058%2C642%20vacancies%20have%20been%20notified%20for%20recruitment%20in%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railways%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20neglected%20throughout%20the%20Congress%20rule.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20considered%20a%20political%20tool%2C%20not%20a%20department%20which%20can%20bring%20about%20a%20big%20change%20in%20people's%20lives.%20That%20is%20the%20change%20which%20has%20happened%20during%20PM%20Modi's%20tenure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeeting%20High%20Demand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20rail%20travel%20is%20increasing%20every%20day%20and%20the%20government%20is%20bringing%20about%20a%20massive%20augmentation%20of%20its%20infrastructure%20to%20meet%20this%20demand%2C%20Ms%20Vaishnaw%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20manufacturing%20of%20trains%20has%20significantly%20increased%20if%20you%20compare%20it%20with%20the%20UPA%20period.%20We%20are%20now%20manufacturing%20close%20to%206%2C000%20coaches%20a%20year.%20During%20UPA%2C%20it%20was%202000-3000%2C%20close%20to%201200%20locomotives%20are%20now%20being%20manufactured%2C%20compared%20to%20200-300%20a%20year%20during%20UPA.%20Massive%20change%20has%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20festive%20season%20round%20the%20corner%2C%20the%20Railways%20has%20decided%20to%20deploy%20a%20record%20number%20of%20special%20trains%20to%20tackle%20the%20rush%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20people%20from%20low-income%20groups%2C%20we%20have%20introduced%20Amrit%20Bharat%20trains%20with%20the%20same%20features%20as%20Vande%20Bharat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20two%20such%20trains%20were%20launched%20in%20January%20and%20one%20will%20be%20launched%20every%20week%20from%20October%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVande%20Bharat%20vs%20Other%20Trains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounting%20the%20charge%20that%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20is%20promoting%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20other%20trains%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOther%20trains%20are%20absolutely%20(getting)%20much%20higher%20focus%20compared%20to%20Vande%20Bharat.%20It's%20just%20that%20Vande%20Bharat%20is%20catching%20the%20imagination%20of%20the%20people.%20That's%20why%20there%20is%20so%20much%20excitement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20as%20Railways%20are%20very%20much%20focused%20on%20making%20sure%20that%20the%20lowest%20income%20categories%20of%20the%20society%20get%20very%20affordable%20rail%20travel%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2016%20new%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20had%20been%20launched%20in%20the%2010%20days%20of%20Modi%203.0%20and%20the%20first%2020-coach%20Vande%20Bharat%20has%20been%20rolled%20out.%20Vande%20Bharat%20sleeper%20trains%20are%20going%20for%20testing%20and%20trials%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BHuge%20Focus%20On%20Safety%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20repeatedly%20criticised%20Mr%20Vaishnaw%20over%20the%20Railways'%20safety%20record%20and%20train%20derailments.%20Responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20how%20the%20national%20transporter%20plans%20to%20tackle%20safety%20issues%2C%20the%20minister%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20sure%20that%20each%20and%20every%20incident%20that%20happens%20in%20Railways%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20an%20accident%20or%20other%20incident%2C%20we%20go%20to%20the%20root%20cause.%20Wherever%20systemic%20changes%20have%20to%20be%20made%2C%20we%20make%20them%2C%20wherever%20procedural%20improvements%20have%20to%20be%20done%2C%20we%20do%20that%2C%20and%20where%20technology%20has%20to%20be%20changed%2C%20we%20are%20changing%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20done%2097%2C000%20inspections%2C%20verified%2090%2C000%20signal%20plans%2C%202%2C500%20km%20of%20tracks%20(have%20been)%20renewed.%20Ultrasound%20testing%20is%20being%20done%20for%20the%20entire%20railway%20network.%20This%20fiscal%2C%201%2C86%2C000%20km%20of%20tracks%20have%20been%20checked%20with%20ultrasound%20machines%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20stressing%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20focus%20on%20safety%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Centre's%20much-touted%20Kavach%20train%20protection%20system%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20Congress%20governments%20could%20not%20do%20in%2058%20years%2C%20within%20a%20short%20time-frame%20of%2010%20years%2C%20we%20got%20this%20new%20technology%20developed%2C%20tested%20and%20the%20deployment%20started.%20The%20first%20tender%20was%20done%20in%202022%2C%20out%20of%20that%20632%20km%20is%20already%20commissioned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVersion%204%20of%20Kavach%20was%20approved%20on%20July%2016%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20government%20has%20put%20out%20tenders%20for%2010%2C000%20locomotives%20and%209%2C600%20km%20of%20train%20trains.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20happy%20to%20share%20that%20yesterday%2C%20the%20first%20section%20with%20Kavach%204.0%20got%20commissioned%20between%20Kota%20and%20Sawai%20Madhopur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20with%20the%20system%20in%20place%2C%20the%20driver%20can%20see%20the%20signal%20from%20several%20kilometres%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20a%20timeline%20for%20this%20system%20being%20implemented%20across%20the%20Railway%20network%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20countries%20which%20have%20half%20or%20less%20than%20half%20of%20our%20network%20size%20took%20about%2015.20%20years.%20But%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20given%20us%20a%20very%20aggressive%20target.%20We%20would%20like%20to%20cover%20the%20whole%20network%20within%205-6%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726570740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fc6ldch6o_ashwini-vaishnaw-interview_625x300_17_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashwini-vaishnaw-interview-huge-focus-on-safety-railways-ministers-report-on-modi-3-0s-100-days-6585558%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20set%20an%20aggressive%20target%20for%20implementing%20the%20Kavach%20train%20protection%20system%20across%20the%20rail%20network%20in%20the%20next%20five%20to%20six%20years%2C%20Railways%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20told%20NDTV%20as%20Modi%203.0%20completed%20100%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashwini-vaishnaw-interview-huge-focus-on-safety-railways-ministers-report-on-modi-3-0s-100-days-6585558%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2217-Year-Old%20Cheerleader%20From%20'America's%20Got%20Talent'%20Dies%20By%20Suicide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E17-year-old%20Emily%20Gold%2C%20a%20talented%20dancer%20and%20cheerleader%20from%20California%2C%20who%20com