22%3ETEPCO%20has%20suspended%20efforts%20to%20extract%20highly%20radioactive%20material%20from%20Japan's%20Fukushima%20nuclear%20plant%20due%20to%20a%20technical%20problem%20with%20remote%20cameras.%20This%20extraction%20is%20essential%20for%20decommissioning%20the%20facility%2C%20which%20was%20severely%20damaged%20by%20a%20tsunami%20in%202011.%20Engineers%20must%20resolve%20this%20issue%20before%20continuing%20the%20operation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-suspends-trial-removal-of-fukushima-nuclear-debris%2Farticleshow%2F113424085.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-suspends-trial-removal-of-fukushima-nuclear-debris%2Famp_articleshow%2F113424085.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapan-suspends-trial-removal-of-fukushima-nuclear-debris%2Famp_articleshow%2F113424085.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Best%20Dhabas%20To%20Save%20on%20Your%20Maps%20for%20the%20Next%20Road%20Trip%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EI%20distinctly%20recall%20a%202019%20college%20road%20trip%20to%20Kasara%20which%20lies%20along%20the%20Mumbai-Nashik%20route.%20The%20plan%20was%20an%20overnight%20trek%20to%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Sandhan%20Valley%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20Valley%20of%20Shadows).%20We%20decided%20to%20fuel%20up%20before%20commencing%20the%20long%20walk%20through%20the%20ravine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20local%20food%20joint%2C%20piping%20hot%20Maggi%2C%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20savoury%20Indian%20pastry)%2C%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pavs%3C%2Fem%3E%20(deep%20fried%20potato%20dumplings%20in%20bread)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoccupied%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20the%20ricketty%20table%20as%2017%20hungry%20adolescents%20feasted%20to%20their%20heart%E2%80%99s%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManners%20and%20etiquette%20waltzed%20out%20through%20the%20window%20as%20we%20smacked%20our%20lips%20and%20licked%20the%20spicy%20Maharashtrian%20garlic%20%3Cem%3Echutney%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoff%20our%20fingers.%20It%20became%20clear%20to%20me%20why%20since%20time%20immemorial%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360331%2Fnational-highway-restaurants-food-joints-expressway-karnal-haveli-amrik-sukhdev-azad-hind-dhaba%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edhabas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(roadside%20food%20stalls)%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20the%20first%20choice%20of%20truck%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresumably%2C%20the%20first%20instances%20of%20%3Cem%3Edhabas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eappeared%20around%20the%20middle%20of%20the%2020th%20century%20on%20Grand%20Trunk%20Road%20(one%20of%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20roads%20that%20connects%20Central%20Asia%20to%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent).%20I%20can%20vividly%20imagine%20a%20bunch%20of%20truckers%20sitting%20around%20on%20%3Cem%3Echarpaayis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(cots)%2C%20digging%20into%20%3Cem%3Eparanthas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20Punjabi%20speciality)%2C%20and%20gulping%20down%20glasses%20of%20%3Cem%3Elassi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sweetened%20milk)%20as%20empty%20plates%20were%20cleared%2C%20making%20room%20for%20more%20helpings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Edhaba%20%3C%2Fem%3Eculture%20still%20persists%20and%2C%20whether%20you%20recall%20or%20not%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20had%20a%20slice%20of%20it.%20Here%20are%20eight%20%3Cem%3Edhabas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eyou%20may%20want%20to%20check%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Chilika%20Dhaba%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20seafood%20is%20where%20your%20heart%20lies%2C%20then%20the%20Chilika%20Dhaba%20(located%20near%20its%20namesake%20lake)%20in%20Barkul%2C%20Odisha%2C%20is%20where%20you%20should%20be%20heading.%20Spicy%20curry%20seeps%20out%20of%20vibrant%20crab%20shells%2C%20soaking%2