20an%20election%20mode%2C%20and%20that%20means%20that%20any%20step%20that%20might%20disadvantage%20the%20Democratic%20presidential%20candidate%20cannot%20be%20taken.%20After%20supporting%20a%20proxy%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20against%20Russia%20all%20this%20while%2C%20any%20step%20to%20de-escalate%20or%20open%20the%20doors%20to%20negotiation%20would%20be%20almost%20impossible%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20is%20between%20escalating%20or%20avoiding%20any%20serious%20new%20escalatory%20step.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20the%20discussion%20over%20allowing%20Zelenskyy%20to%20use%20NATO-supplied%20long-range%20missiles%20to%20strike%20deep%20into%20Russian%20territory%20comes%20in.%20Ukraine%20is%20already%20striking%20deep%20into%20Russia%20with%20drones%20and%20has%20also%20launched%20a%20land%20invasion%20of%20Russia%20in%20Kursk.%20But%20for%20Russia%2C%20it%20will%20mean%20a%20major%20escalation%20by%20NATO%20if%20the%20UK-supplied%20Storm%20Shadow%20cruise%20missiles%20were%20used%20against%20Russia%20itself%2C%20although%20they%20have%20been%20used%20against%20Ukrainian%20territories%20that%20Russia%20has%20annexed.%20Russia%20has%20in%20practice%20accepted%20that%20distinction%20and%20not%20raised%20the%20stakes%20as%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20has%20now%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUK%20Determined%20To%20Escalate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20president%20has%20warned%20that%20such%20a%20move%20will%20mean%20NATO%20entering%20into%20a%20direct%20conflict%20with%20Russia%20as%20these%20missiles%20cannot%20be%20launched%20without%20guidance%20by%20US%20satellites%20and%2C%20indeed%2C%20by%20NATO%20crews%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%20would%20not%20know%20how%20to%20prime%20them%20technically%20for%20targeting.%20Putin%20has%20declared%20that%20Russia%20will%20take%20appropriate%20steps%20to%20counter%20this%20escalation.%20What%20this%20could%20mean%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20speculation%20as%20Russia%20could%20have%20options%20below%20the%20nuclear%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%2C%20as%20usual%2C%20is%20determined%20to%20escalate%20the%20conflict.%20Five%20of%20its%20ex-Defence%20Secretaries%20want%20Ukraine%20to%20be%20given%20permission%20to%20use%20long-range%20weapons%20even%20without%20the%20US's%20approval.%20The%20UK's%20deep-seated%20hostility%20towards%20Russia%20seems%20almost%20compulsive.%20Its%20excessive%20warmongering%20could%20also%20be%20to%20both%20push%20the%20US%20to%20escalate%20while%20also%20acting%20as%20a%20willing%20front%20for%20the%20US%20to%20make%20the%20latter%20look%20more%20%26quot%3Bresponsible%26quot%3B.%20The%20US%2C%20which%20is%20ultimately%20responsible%20for%20managing%20the%20consequences%20of%20escalation%2C%20and%20not%20Europe%2C%20seems%20hesitant%20to%20allow%20the%20use%20of%20its%20long-range%20missiles%20to%20strike%20deep%20into%20Russia%20but%20seems%20prepared%20to%20clear%20the%20use%20of%20British%20and%20French%20missiles.%20The%20fiction%20would%20be%20that%20the%20US%20would%20not%20be%20directly%20involved%2C%20though%20when%20Putin%20refers%20to%20NATO%20being%20involved%20-%20as%20these%20missiles%20need%20NATO%20technical%20support%20for%20launching%20them%20-%20he%20is%20implicating%20the%20US%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Western%20Narrative%20On%20Ukraine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelenskyy's%20strategy%20seems%20to%20be%20to%20drag%20NATO%20more%20and%20more%20into%20the%20conflict%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20eventual%20cost%20is%20for%20Ukraine%20or%20for%20Europe%2C%20as%20the%20survival%20of%20his%20own%20regime%20is%20involved.%20The%20Western%20narrative%20on%20Ukraine%20is%20simple%3A%20Russia%20has%20violated%20the%20sovereignty%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20a%20smaller%20European%20country%3B%20the%20attack%20is%20unprovoked%20and%20violates%20the%20international%20order%3B%20if%20Russia%20were%20to%20succeed%20it%20would%20next%20threaten%20Western%20Europe%3B%20Russia%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20win%2C%20and%20therefore%20Ukraine%20has%20to%20be%20supported.%20Zelenskyy%20has%20exploited%20this%20simplistic%20narrative%20to%20seek%20more%20and%20more%20arms%20from%20the%20West%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20Ukrainian%20fight%20but%20a%20European%20one.%20He%20is%20now%20intending%20to%20go%20to%20the%20US%20to%20discuss%20his%20%26quot%3Bvictory%20plan%26quot%3B%20with%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20Europe%20openly%20seek%20to%20use%20this%20conflict%20to%20impose%20a%20strategic%20defeat%20on%20Russia%2C%20and%20if%20that%20looks%20increasingly%20unlikely%20despite%20imposing%20draconian%20sanctions%2C%20then%20to%2C%20at%20least%2C%20continue%20to%20bleed%20and%20weaken%20Russia%20by%20prolonging%20the%20proxy%20war%20against%20it.%20This%20was%20the%20sense%20of%20the%20joint%20Op-Ed%20in%20Financial%20Times%20by%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20intelligence%20chiefs%2C%20which%20stressed%20it%20was%20vital%20to%20continue%20supporting%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20the%20CIA%20chief%20also%20seeing%20virtue%20in%20Ukraine's%20land%20attack%20against%20Russia%20in%20Kursk.%20The%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20and%20the%20UK%20Foreign%20Secretary%20also%20jointly%20visited%20Kyiv%20very%20recently%20and%20announced%20more%20financial%20aid%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20background%20that%20India%20is%20seeking%20to%20play%20some%20role%20to%20nudge%20the%20two%20sides%20towards%20a%20negotiated%20solution%20to%20the%20conflict.%20India%20has%20not%20been%20deterred%20from%20taking%20this%20initiative%20despite%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20seemingly%20irreconcilable%20position%20of%20the%20two%20sides%20on%20some%20fundamental%20points%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20any%20peace%20effort%20with%20Russia%20and%20Ukraine%20cannot%20move%20forward%20without%20the%20US.%20We%20have%20not%20announced%20contact%20with%20the%20US%20on%20this%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActually%2C%20Europe%20will%20have%20to%20be%20involved%20too%20if%20India%20wants%20to%20play%20a%20substantive%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Modi%20will%20discuss%20India's%20initiative%20with%20Biden%20when%20he%20goes%20to%20the%20US%20this%20month%20is%20likely%2C%20now%20that%20he%20knows%20Putin's%20mind%20after%20his%20own%20talks%20with%20him%20and%20the%20feedback%20he%20has%20got%20from%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval.%20But%20Biden%20can%20hardly%20modify%20its%20position%20in%20favour%20of%20dialogue%20and%20diplomacy%20with%20the%20US%20presidential%20election%20in%20the%20offing%20when%20all%20along%20the%20choice%20has%20been%20to%20wage%20a%20proxy%20war%20against%20Russia%20for%20larger%20geopolitical%20reasons%20that%20go%20beyond%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rhetoric%20against%20Russia%20has%20gone%20up%2C%20with%20accusations%20against%20the%20Russian%20spread%20of%20disinformation%20in%20the%20US%20and%20globally%2C%20and%20the%20effort%20to%20seek%20a%20worldwide%20ban%20on%20%3Cem%3ERT%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20related%20Russian%20media%20for%20intelligence%20activities%2C%20etc.%20With%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20visiting%20India%20shortly%2C%20Modi%20will%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20discuss%20his%20peace%20initiative%20with%20him%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoval's%20Visit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20raised%20its%20peacemaking%20profile%20by%20Modi%20sending%20Doval%20to%20St%20Petersburg%20to%20personally%20brief%20Putin%20on%20the%20talk%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20with%20Zelenskyy%20in%20Kyiv.%20Despite%20the%20controversial%20comments%20made%20by%20Zelenskyy%20to%20the%20Indian%20press%20on%20India's%20purchase%20of%20Russian%20oil%2C%20calling%20on%20India%20to%20join%20the%20communiqu%26amp%3B%23233%3B%20issued%20after%20the%20first%20summit%20in%20Switzerland%20if%20it%20wanted%20to%20hold%20a%20peace%20summit%2C%20and%20differing%20perspectives%20on%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20next%20peace%20summit%20that%20came%20out%20in%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Jaishankar's%20press%20briefing%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20enough%20of%20substance%20seems%20to%20have%20emerged%20from%20the%20private%20talks%20with%20Zelenskyy%20to%20warrant%20a%20personal%20briefing%20to%20Putin.%20Is%20it%20that%20the%20Ukrainian%20position%20in%20private%20is%20less%20rigid%20on%20substantive%20issues%20than%20its%20public%20enunciation%3F%20By%20accepting%20to%20receive%20Doval%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20gesture%2C%20Putin%20is%20endorsing%20India's%20peace%20efforts%2C%20though%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20imagine%20that%20he%20would%20resign%20from%20his%20core%20position%20on%20territory%20and%20NATO%20membership%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudging%20from%20what%20the%20Ukrainian%20ambassador%20to%20India%20said%20subsequently%20to%20the%20press%20here%20on%20India's%20peace%20efforts%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20Ukraine%20continues%20to%20aggressively%20define%20its%20position.%20The%20ambassador%20was%20out%20of%20line%20in%20asking%20India%20to%20convince%20Moscow%20to%20join%20peace%20talks%2C%20linking%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20India's%20bid%20for%20permanent%20membership%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20to%20taking%20a%20position%20of%20its%20own%20on%20global%20issues%20and%20not%20simply%20conveying%20messages%20from%20one%20side%20to%20the%20other%20and%20being%20a%20courier%20or%20messenger%20or%20a%20post%20box.%20He%20reiterated%20Zelenskyy's%20position%20that%20the%20condition%20for%20India%20to%20hold%20the%20next%20peace%20summit%20would%20be%20to%20join%20the%20Burgenstock%20communique%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20judge%20the%20dynamics%20of%20the%20peace%20initiative%20India%20has%20taken%20as%20the%20hurdles%20to%20peace%20are%20all%20too%20apparent%20at%20pr