aign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EManisha%20was%20a%20gifted%20child.%20She%20excelled%20at%20activities%20like%20drawing%2C%20dancing%2C%20sports%2C%20and%20singing.%20However%2C%20discouragement%20from%20her%20teachers%20left%20her%20feeling%20excluded%2C%20and%20her%20love%20for%20these%20activities%20was%20left%20in%20the%20lurch%20%E2%80%94%20only%20because%20of%20how%20she%20looked.%20%E2%80%9CI%20protested%20but%20no%20one%20helped.%20The%20discrimination%20made%20me%20change%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManisha%E2%80%99s%20life%20took%20a%20turn%20when%20she%20joined%20a%20new%20school%20and%20found%20friends%20and%20teachers%20who%20helped%20her%20regain%20her%20confidence.%20Drawing%20became%20her%20refuge.%20Channelling%20her%20pain%20into%20her%20art%2C%20she%20brought%20life%20into%20portraits%20that%20soon%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20many.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20those%20traumatic%20times%2C%20art%20helped%20me%20heal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20illustrations%2C%20particularly%20of%20celebrities%2C%20soon%20caught%20attention%2C%20going%20viral%20across%20social%20media.%20She%20fondly%20remembers%20one%20of%20her%20proudest%20moments%3A%20The%20day%20she%20gifted%20a%20portrait%20to%20Bollywood%20actress%20Deepika%20Padukone%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331304%2Fdevanshi-yadav-shaheed-ramashray-welfare-society-bareilly-acid-attack-sexual-abuse-survivor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20role%20in%20the%20film%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EChhapaak%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManisha%E2%80%99s%20journey%20didn%E2%80%99t%20end%20there.%20She%20expanded%20her%20creative%20space%20by%20posting%20makeover%20videos%20on%20Instagram%2C%20boldly%20challenging%20traditional%20beauty%20standards.%20While%20she%20faced%20mockery%20from%20many%2C%20her%20family%20stood%20as%20her%20rock%2C%20helping%20her%20rise%20above%20the%20negativity.%20Gradually%2C%20her%20art%20also%20became%20a%20source%20of%20income%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Manisha%20is%20not%20just%20an%20influencer%20but%20an%20inspiration%2C%20with%20thousands%20of%20fans%20who%20admire%20her%20courage%20and%20creativity.%20For%20those%20who%20send%20negativity%20her%20way%2C%20her%20response%20is%20graceful%20and%20simple%3A%20%E2%80%9CThanks%20for%20motivating%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726498118000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D366103%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manisha%20Prajapati%2C%20known%20as%20Mannu%2C%20was%20just%20four%20when%20a%20tragic%20accident%20left%20her%20with%20severe%20burns.%20Defying%20societal%20rejection%2C%20she%20turned%20to%20art%20for%20healing%20and%20now%20challenges%20conventional%20beauty%20standards%20through%20her%20powerful%20social%20media%20presence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Khushi%20Arora%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366103%2Fmanisha-marodia-prajapati-make-up-artist-burn-survivor-victim-social-media-content-creator-journey-story-watch-video-chhapaak-deepika-padukone%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20are%20the%20polls%20showing%20after%20another%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20Trump%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726496040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F09%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-daily-podcast-160924_6687591.png%3F20240916143145%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwhat-are-the-polls-showing-after-another-assassination-attempt-on-trump-13216239%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Donald%20Tr