ttps%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F239559%2Fips-hero-free-upsc-coaching-nagaland-pritpal-kaur-batra-tuensang-noklak-district-drugs-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren%20of%20Nagaland%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20other%20states%20for%20medical%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20am%20intrigued.%20Does%20this%20circumstance%20go%20beyond%20a%20travel%20inconvenience%3F%20I%20decided%20to%20check%20with%20Zavi.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20affirms.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20heard%20from%20some%20friends%20and%20seniors%20who%20have%20moved%20to%20Rajasthan%20and%20Gujarat%20that%20they%20face%20instances%20of%20discrimination%20because%20of%20their%20appearance.%20They%20tell%20me%20how%20their%20peers%20put%20up%20boundaries%20and%20aren%E2%80%99t%20very%20friendly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Zavi%20assures%20me%20that%20the%20discrimination%20does%20not%20cross%20the%20line%20and%20is%20not%20of%20a%20serious%20nature%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20maintain%20that%20staying%20in%20our%20own%20state%20and%20having%20local%20friends%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20those%20of%20us%20who%20study%20in%20Nagaland.%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Soumya%20had%20heard%20these%20stories%20from%20friends%20of%20hers%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20Northeast.%20And%20soon%2C%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20solution%20overrode%20every%20other%20priority%20of%20hers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-1-1725974857.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Soumya%20Chakraborty%20(L)%3B%20Nagaland%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Research%20(NIMSR)%20(R)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-1-1725