0woman%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20a%20leader.%20A%20woman%E2%80%99s%20absence%20from%20the%20family%20for%20a%20certain%20period%20of%20time%20should%20not%20make%20much%20of%20a%20difference%20because%20every%20person%20in%20the%20family%20should%20bear%20the%20ownership%20as%20an%20equal%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Soumya%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20a%20woman%20decides%20to%20do%20something%2C%20there%20are%20bound%20to%20be%20100%20questions%20and%20200%20%E2%80%98no%E2%80%99s.%20But%20if%20her%20mind%20says%20even%20one%20%E2%80%98yes%E2%80%99%2C%20she%20should%20go%20for%20it.%E2%80%9D%20Considering%20herself%20fortunate%20for%20having%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%2C%20husband%E2%80%99s%20and%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20full%20support%2C%20Dr%20Soumya%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20take%20up%20these%20adventures.%20I%20knew%20until%20and%20unless%20I%20put%20myself%20forward%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20never%20know%20if%20I%20was%20capable%20of%20navigating%20these%20roles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-2-1725974926.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20students%20during%20a%20practical%20session%20at%20NIMSR.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-2-1725974926.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-2-1725974926-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-2-1725974926-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-2-1725974926-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-2-1725974926-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365393%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20curriculum%20at%20the%20Nagaland%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Research%20(NIMSR)%20is%20in%20line%20with%20that%20of%20the%20National%20Medical%20Commission.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%20Acknowledging%20that%20she%20often%20finds%20it%20tricky%20to%20balance%20her%20professional%20and%20personal%20life%20as%20a%20mother%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20have%20been%20blessed%20with%20support%20and%20help.%20When%20my%20daughter%20was%20younger%2C%20evenings%20were%20a%20tough%20time.%20She%20would%20want%20me%20with%20her.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20mobile%20phones%20weren%E2%80%99t%20as%20popular.%20And%20there%20was%20little%20I%20could%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20the%20dilemmas%20and%20the%20impasses%2C%20Dr%20Soumya%20encourages%20women%20to%20never%20put%20their%20dreams%20on%20the%20back%20burner.%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20is%20impossible%20in%20this%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20that%20being%20said%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20you%20who%20can%20make%20it%20possible.%E2%80%9D%20She%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F244424%2Fdomestic-abuse-rural-women-empowerment-laxmi-waghmare-cii-inspiring-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eencourages%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20their%20life%20purpose.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20everyone%20loves%20setting%20up%20a%20college.%20You%20may%20have%20different%20dreams%2C%20but%20you%20need%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20move%20beyond%20where%20you%20are%20to%20find%20your%20breakthrough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20is%20insistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20these%20ideals%20backing%20her%2C%20Dr%20Soumya%20took%20the%20reins%20of%20developing%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20first%20medical%20college.%20The%2012th%20of%20December%202022%20will%20always%20be%20a%20day%20etched%20in%20her%20memory%20as%20it%20was%20the%20day%20she%20set%20foot%20in%20the%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENavigating%20a%20new%20landscape%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20morning%20as%20Dr%20Soumya%20walks%20into%20the%20anatomy%20class%20to%20see%20enthusiastic%20faces%2C%20she%20says%20it%20is%20all%20the%20validation%20she%20seeks.%20%E2%80%9CI%20see%20gratitude%20on%20their%20faces.%E2%80%9D%20Currently%2C%20100%20students%20are%20studying%20at%20the%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20well-oiled%20wheels%20of%20the%20institute%20are%20chugging%20well%2C%20when%20Dr%20Soumya%20first%20started%2C%20the%20scene%20was%20contrastingly%20different.%20One%20of%20the%20things%20that%20baffled%20her%20the%20most%20was%20the%20topography%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20this%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20mountain%20terrain.%20Nagaland%20is%20one%20of%20the%20farthest%20Northeast%20hilly%20states.%20While%20setting%20up%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347460%2Fdaily-wager-doctor-builds-school-utkal-gaurav-international-odisha-started-village-pradeep-sethi-admission%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfrastructure%20of%20the%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20realised%20these%20were%20sinking%20zones%20%E2%80%94%20areas%20made%20of%20red%20soil%20and%20no%20stones.%20So%2C%20we%20needed%20a%20new%20construction%20pattern.%20Each%20time%20we%20would%20try%20constructing%2C%20water%20would%20begin%20gushing%20out%20of%20the%20earth.%E2%80%9D%20The%20team%20then%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20retention%20walls%20to%20support%20the%20construction.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%