india.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445-150x188.webp%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FIMG_20230423_110238_478-1726233445.webp%20736w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365885%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Lobzang%20Chorol%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20this%20fascination%20and%20concern%20that%20motivated%20her%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20cold%20desert%E2%80%99s%20water%20systems%20to%20pursue%20her%20PhD%20at%20IIT-ISM%20(Indian%20School%20of%20Mines)%2C%20Dhanbad.%20Under%20the%20mentorship%20of%20Professor%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20a%20leading%20expert%20in%20the%20field%2C%20she%20closely%20studied%20the%20groundwater%20systems%20in%20Leh%20town.%20Spanning%20six%20years%20and%20eight%20months%2C%20her%20research%20finally%20culminated%20in%20the%20completion%20of%20her%20thesis%20earlier%20this%20year.%20(You%20can%20find%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fprofile%2FLobzang-Chorol%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20times%20when%20the%20challenges%20seemed%20overwhelming%20%E2%80%94%20from%20people%20unwilling%20to%20give%20their%20borewell%20water%20samples%20to%20collecting%20secondary%20baseline%20data%20and%20the%20emotional%20weight%20of%20seeing%20the%20deterioration%20of%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20water%20resources%20firsthand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20every%20time%20I%20felt%20discouraged%2C%20I%20remembered%20the%20faces%20of%20my%20family%20and%20community%20back%20in%20Ladakh%2C%20depending%20on%20this%20precious%20resource.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20academic%20research%3B%20it%20was%20about%20the%20lives%20and%20futures%20of%20real%20people.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20earning%20a%20degree%3B%20it%20was%20about%20securing%20a%