0%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Plugzmart)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725976650000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FPlugzsmart-Image-3-1725974308.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D365359%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chennai-based%20Plugzmart%20secured%20ARAI%20certification%20for%20its%2060kW%20DC%20fast%20charger%2C%20marking%20a%20key%20step%20in%20advancing%20India%E2%80%99s%20electric%20vehicle%20infrastructure.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20charger%E2%80%99s%20proprietary%20controller%20enhances%20compatibility%2C%20safety%2C%20and%20high-speed%20charging%20capabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20Startup%20%E2%80%98Fulva%E2%80%99%2C%204%20Friends%20Take%2024%20Types%20of%20Kozhikoden%20Halwa%20to%20The%20World%3B%20Earn%20Rs%2084%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHamza%20Shaheem%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Kozhikode%2C%20recalls%20the%20very%20first%20time%20he%20was%20treated%20to%20a%20particular%20red%20sweet%20from%20a%20bakery%20near%20his%20home%20in%20Feroke.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20so%20good!%E2%80%9D%20he%20exclaims%20as%20he%20retrieves%20the%20memory%20from%20a%20treasure%20trove%20of%20others%2C%20all%20involving%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20that%20childhood%20experience%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308752%2Fdodha-barfi-history-story-of-wrestler-harbans-vig-tales-of-taste-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20confectionery%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20out%20of%20flour%2C%20butter%2C%20milk%20and%20sugar)%20became%20an%20important%20guest%20at%20Shaheem%E2%80%99s%20home.%20It%20was%20the%20main%20celebrant%20on%20special%20occasions.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20included%20festivals%20and%20dinners%20when%20relatives%20would%20drop%20by%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20smile%20that%20suggests%20he%20would%20gladly%20binge%20on%20the%20dessert%20every%20day%20if%20he%20could%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eaficionado%20says%20it%20formed%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20growing-up%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20question%20begs%20to%20be%20asked%20why%20the%20natives%20of%20Kozhikode%20hold%20a%20reverence%20for%20this%20sweet.%20Shaheem%20credits%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20simple%20but%20unique%20taste.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20considered%20as%20an%20icon%20of%20Kerala%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Childhood%20friends%20(from%20L%20to%20R)%20Shabas%20Ahamed%20N%20C%2C%20Thesreef%20Ali%20P%20K%2C%20Sanu%20Muhammed%20C%20and%20Irfan%20Safar%20S%20started%20Fulva%20to%20retail%20authentic%20Kerala%20specialities%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-1725528358-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364549%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChildhood%20friends%20(from%20L%20to%20R)%20Shabas%20Ahamed%20N%20C%2C%20Thesreef%20Ali%20P%20K%2C%20Sanu%20Muhammed%20C%20and%20Irfan%20Safar%20S%20started%20Fulva%20to%20retail%20authentic%20Kerala%20specialities%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20idolises%20the%20red%20variant%20(also%20the%20most%20popular%20flavour)%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eenjoys%20a%20gamut%20of%20flavour%20quotients.%20And%20understandably%2C%20Shaheem%20considers%20himself%20lucky%20to%20have%20lived%20and%20grown%20up%20in%20a%20city%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20mass-manufactured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20as%20fortunate.%20So%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20divulge%20an%20important%20piece%20of%20information.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20limited%20to%20Kozhikode%20anymore%20to%20get%20your%20fill%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Not%20just%20one%2C%20but%20an%20eclectic%20mix%20of%2024%20varieties%20will%20find%20their%20way%20to%20your%20doorstep%20if%20you%20wish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20brainwave%20by%20four%20childhood%20friends%20is%20making%20this%20possible.%20Their%20startup%20Fulva%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Kerala-based%20brand%20serving%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F286270%2Fmom-sells-authentic-maharashtrian-food-in-mumbai-pune-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthentic%20traditional%20food%20products%20%3C%2Fa%3Esourced%20from%20small-scale%20producers%20%E2%80%94%20is%20completing%20a%20year%20of%20operations%20and%20has%20already%20touched%20a%20milestone%20with%20a%20Rs%2084%20lakh%20turnover.%20And%20as%20they%20share%2C%20their%20success%20story%20is%20written%20by%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESquare-shaped%20pieces%20of%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20visited%20Kozhikode%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20know%20it%20is%20almost%20a%20sacrilege%20to%20not%20return%20home%20with%20servings%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20also%20considered%20a%20%E2%80%98prestige%20symbol%E2%80%99%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20history%20tells%20us%2C%20has%20an%20interesting%20story%20that%20prequels%20its%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20supposedly%20an%20Arab%20invention%20born%20around%20the%2016th%20century%20when%20the%20community%20settled%20in%20Kerala.%20They%20were%20intent%20on%20gifting%20a%20piece%20of%20their%20culinary%20prowess%20to%20Kozhikode%E2%80%99s%20Zamorin%20(monarch).%20And%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Emade%20the%20cut.%20It%20went%20on%20to%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20spice%20trade%20and%20eventually%20part%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20gastronomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20been%20perplexed%20as%20to%20how%20a%20simple%20blend%20of%20water%2C%20sugar%2C%20corn%20starch%2C%20coconut%20oil%2C%20citrus%20salt%2C%20and%20flavourings%20birthed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F281110%2Fmithai-map-of-india-10-lesser-known-indian-sweets-you-must-try-at-least-once%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20dessert%20so%20exquisite%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20no%20successor%20dessert%20could%20compete%20with.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20said%20that%20no%20two%20blocks%20of%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20the%20same%20as%20the%20ratio%20of%20each%20ingredient%20varies%20from%20proprietor%20to%20proprietor%20in%20Kozhikode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20tourists%20and%20locals%20aren%E2%80%99t%20picky%20about%20these%20changing%20nuances%20so%20long%20as%20they%20get%20their%20fill%20of%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%