20these%20signs%20to%20help%20others%20recognise%20when%20someone%20may%20be%20silently%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecognising%20the%20warning%20signs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20on%2010%20September%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311837%2Fengineer-quit-us-job-to-launch-villa-mart-mobile-mandi-farmer-suicides-fair-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Suicide%20Prevention%20Day%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20observed%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20prevent%20suicides.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20theme%20set%20by%20the%20International%20Association%20for%20Suicide%20Prevention%20(IASP)%20is%20%E2%80%98Changing%20the%20Narrative%20on%20Suicide%E2%80%99%2C%20with%20a%20call%20to%20action%20to%20%E2%80%98Start%20the%20Conversation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%2C%20according%20to%20IASP%2C%20is%20to%20shift%20how%20people%20perceive%20suicide%20and%20encourage%20open%20conversations%20about%20suicidal%20behaviour%20among%20communities%2C%20governments%2C%20individuals%2C%20organisations%2C%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20reports%20that%20over%207%2C20%2C000%20people%20die%20by%20suicide%20each%20year%20globally.%20An%20equal%20or%20even%20greater%20number%20attempt%20to%20take%20their%20own%20lives.%20This%20highlights%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20being%20alert%2C%20present%2C%20and%20supportive%20of%20loved%20ones%20who%20may%20be%20struggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FInfographic-website-41-1725952202.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22What%20to%20do%20if%20someone%20contemplating%20suicide%20comes%20to%20you%20for%20help%3F%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3